C:/> TAIL.APP -5 ODYSSEY.TXT
shirt he gave it to the good old woman, who folded it tidily up, and hung it
for him over a peg by his bed side, after which she went out, pulled the door
to by a silver catch, and drew the bolt home by means of the strap. But
